channel.title: 525 running problem
channel.description:
So i am starting a 525 server, and this keeps coming up, it's disallowing me to access, but with other sources, i can. Please note this is my first time working with this version of server, just simply help me if you can/wish, and i'm going to be fine.
Here's the problem
[code][2009/09/14 18:28:52] [AnonymousIoService-1]: New session from: /(MY IP ADDRESS):2515 [2009/09/14 18:28:52] [AnonymousIoService-1]: Session has been closed: /(MY IP ADDRESS):2515[/code]
So basically what i see is that it's denying me from accessing it, yet the server is running, and the client server status says it's online, although this happens. It's not liek it always happens, i can connect to some, but sometimes this pops up, any help or ideas.
